<h1>Free Returns</h1>

<p>Fact:  In 2013, less than 1% of our customers returned their photograph(s).  If you are still undecided on purchasing a photograph, the odds are on your side.</p>

<p>If for any reason you are not 100% satisfied, you can return any photograph free of charge and then you will receive a full refund ( including the cost of tax & initial shipping ).</p>

<h2>Our Return Policy</h2>

<p>Please notify us within 14 calendar days (not business days) of when you received the package and we will send you a free return shipping label.  You will be ineligible for free return shipping if we are contacted past that time period.</p>

<h2 class='return_divider'>Instructions For A Return</h2>
<p>Email us at <span class='email_link'><%= mail_to 'horschgallery@gmail.com', nil, subject: 'HorschGallery Return' %></span> and fill out the remaining details in the body of the email.
</p>

