<p class='fixit'>Once we receive your return request we will send you another email with a UPS return shipping label which you can then place on the top of your return package.</p>

<h2>Return Packaging</h2>
<p>Please package the photograph(s) back up in the same (if not similar) fashion as how they were original sent to you by using as much cardboard and/or insulation as possible.  Also, if shipping back a framed photo, please use the cardboard corners which came with the print.</p>

<p>Unfortunately, we will not be able to credit you for the extra packaging you may need such as a new box, bubble wrap, cardboard etc.   However, as mentioned above, we will pay for the entire return USP shipping fee back to our warehouse.</p>

